1
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,200
Right.

2
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:33,280
These are your mother's initial medical records.

3
00:01:35,479 --> 00:01:37,880
Shen Jingyao told me to tear them up.

4
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:41,050
Fearing someone might find out in the future,

5
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:44,039
he made me destroy the evidence in advance.

6
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,720
But I didn't.

7
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,280
First,

8
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,120
my conscience wouldn't allow it.

9
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,920
I felt guilty.

10
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,240
Second,

11
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,940
I was afraid he would turn against me,

12
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,100
so I kept it to protect myself.

13
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,770
Is there anything else?

14
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,680
No, nothing else.

15
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,880
Look, I gave you the medical records.

16
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,280
You only have one chance.

17
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,479
I advise you to think it through.

18
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:12,520
Yes, yes, there is.

19
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,320
This is the phone

20
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,640
your mother secretly hid.

21
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,680
During her hospitalization,

22
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,600
Shen Jingyao wanted to control her,

23
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:28,440
so he confiscated her usual phone.

24
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,240
Then your mother used this

25
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:32,720
to contact the outside.

26
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:35,520
Everyone must pay for their sins.

27
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,280
I won't let you off,

28
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,520
but I won't use vigilante justice either.

29
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,920
Every word you just said.

30
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,250
I recorded everything.

31
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:45,880
The police will base on these evidence and testimonies

32
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:49,060
to determine how much responsibility you should bear.

33
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,079
You.

34
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,920
This is

35
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,280
a sin.

36
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,240
Boss, how is my phone?

37
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,680
Fortunately, it's not too old.

38
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,320
The chat records and albums inside,

39
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,120
I have recovered them all.

40
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,380
Then you can go back and read them slowly.

41
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,320
Right.

42
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,440
There is an

43
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,240
encrypted cloud drive in the phone's cloud.

44
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,440
It seems to store a lot of things inside.

45
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,460
You may need a password to open it.

46
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,320
Thanks.

47
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,440
Take care.

48
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,959
It's not a birthday,

49
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,880
or a house number.

50
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,960
What could it be?

51
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:28,680
Stop!

52
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,880
Run! Run!

53
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Let's see where you can run.

54
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,840
Where are you running?

55
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,120
Dad.

56
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,640
You worthless thing.

57
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,480
How do you still have the nerve to come back?

58
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,159
I have thought of many ways.

59
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:40,640
He's just not interested, Dad.

60
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,600
Not interested?

61
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,680
Why don't you think of a way?

62
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,640
You can beg him.

63
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,280
You can get down on your knees.

64
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:50,140
Anyway, I want you to climb into the Lu family's bed.

65
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,440
Dad.

66
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,200
I'm begging you.

67
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,120
Please let me go.

68
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,480
I really don't know how.

69
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,480
I really don't know how.

70
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,720
Cry, cry, cry.

71
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,400
That's all you know how to do.

72
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,960
Just like your dead mother.

73
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,440
Such bad luck.

74
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:10,200
Haven't been to the boxing gym in a while, have you?

75
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,880
Itching for a beating, huh?

76
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,440
Dad.

77
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,760
Have you forgotten the pain?

78
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,760
No, please, no.

79
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,480
Want to know what pain feels like?

80
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,760
No, no.

81
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,080
Dad, I beg you.

82
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,080
Don't send me there.

83
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,240
No, no.

84
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,040
Shen Zhixia, rest assured.

85
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,200
This score,

86
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:30,200
I will definitely settle it with Shen Jingyao for you.

87
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,730
Where did you go?

88
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,000
Feifei.

89
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,720
Shen Zhixia.

90
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,930
How long are you going to play the fool?

91
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,720
Play, hurry.

92
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,640
Seeing me worry about you like this,

93
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,720
is it fun?

94
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,960
Give me a reason.

95
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:50,010
Won't you even give me a reason?

96
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,880
Three days.

97
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:57,720
Give me three more days.

98
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,400
I will tell you everything that happened,

99
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:02,080
from start to finish, without missing a word.

100
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,280
But for these three days,

101
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:09,720
can you help me one last time?

102
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:14,160
Help me protect this amnesiac and foolish version of me.

103
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,440
Shen Zhixia,

104
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,660
you really know how to push your luck.

105
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,480
I know I'm asking for too much.

106
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,520
But,

107
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,880
you're the only one I can rely on.

108
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,860
I only have one condition.

109
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,280
Don't take risks.

110
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,320
Butler.

111
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,540
Pour me a cup of tea.

112
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,960
Butler.

113
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,530
What are you doing here?

114
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,580
I came back to hear a story.

115
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,280
Hear a story?

116
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,679
I think you're really crazy.

117
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:41,080
Staying at the Lu family has driven you mad.

118
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,080
I thought the Lu family kept it well hidden.

119
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,810
Turns out you know everything.

120
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,120
Yes, I am crazy.

121
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,400
So crazy,

122
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:51,460
that it wouldn't even be illegal for me to kill someone.

123
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,840
What exactly do you want?

124
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,720
I told you,

125
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,340
I came back to hear a story.

126
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:00,280
I want to hear the story about you and my mom.

127
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,760
How a poor boy

128
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,680
married into the Lin family

129
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,320
and became the man in charge.

130
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,280
How you step by step

131
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:11,120
drove the woman who loved you to death.

132
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,880
Full of nonsense.

133
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,120
Butler!

134
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,280
Where the hell did you go?

135
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:20,740
Take a guess if there's still anyone on your side in this house.

136
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:28,840
This is my mom's medical record.

137
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,600
It clearly records

138
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,330
how you used clozapine to cause hallucinations.

139
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,540
Don't try to intimidate me with this.

140
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,280
Shen Jingyao approached me.

141
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,120
He gave me 500,000

142
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,920
and asked me, during your mother's every follow-up visit,

143
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:47,440
to secretly increase her dosage.

144
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:51,120
He also made me emphasize in her medical records

145
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:54,720
that her condition kept relapsing

146
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:59,080
and she had severe suicidal tendencies.

147
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,680
If I hand all of these things

148
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,160
over to the police,

149
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:06,170
will you spend the rest of your life in prison?

150
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,040
No.

151
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,640
Please don't.

152
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,880
Listen...

153
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,120
I am your father after all.

154
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:17,120
We share a bond as father and daughter.

155
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,120
Bond?

156
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,000
When you increased my mother's dosage,

157
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,600
did you think about our bond?

158
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,960
When you sent me to the boxing gym,

159
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,880
did you think about our bond?

160
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:31,040
But I am not that unreasonable.

161
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,040
Guess what I brought for you.

162
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:46,010
Don't you want to beg for mercy?

163
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:46,840
Come on,

164
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:49,920
explain clearly to the victim and my mother

165
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:52,680
what you have done to the Lin family all these years.

166
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,880
Kneel down and say it.

167
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,140
I might consider not calling the police.

168
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,400
Kneel!

169
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:14,080
Don't say I didn't give you a chance.

170
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,520
Speak.

171
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:20,840
Yes, I was after the Lin family's money,

172
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,930
so I took the initiative to approach your mother.

173
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,120
After marrying into the family,

174
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,640
relying on my father-in-law's connections,

175
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,720
I did do a lot of projects

176
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,140
and made a lot of money.

177
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:35,280
But people kept calling me a freeloader son-in-law.

178
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,320
I couldn't accept that.

179
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:39,080
Later, I started

180
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:42,440
secretly transferring the company's shares.

181
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,440
I wanted to take all the Lin family's wealth

182
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,760
for myself.

183
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,960
Later, your mother found out,

184
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,020
and she made a fuss.

185
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,240
I thought arguing was pointless.

186
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,600
So I gave her the cold shoulder,

187
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,480
ignored her,

188
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:59,000
and provoked her with the most vicious words.

189
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,360
I just wanted her to know

190
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:01,400
in this house,

191
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,080
who the real master was.

192
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,080
Later,

193
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:10,080
your mother really became a bit abnormal.

194
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:13,260
The doctor said she had depressive tendencies.

195
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,720
I thought my chance had come.

196
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:18,280
If she really went crazy,

197
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,520
the whole company would be mine.

198
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,280
I bribed Li Gang

199
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:27,520
to gradually increase her dosage.

200
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:28,920
Come on, take your medicine.

201
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,040
Take it and you'll get better.

202
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,040
Eat it.

203
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,360
I'm not sick.

204
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,520
Whether you are sick or not

205
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,720
is not up to you.

206
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,720
You need to think of your daughter.

207
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,240
Don't make things difficult for her, hear me?

208
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,160
Come on, eat it.

209
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,240
Eat it.

210
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,040
Eat it, swallow.

211
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,160
Yes, swallow.

212
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,640
Yes, swallow.

213
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:55,880
Let me see.

214
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:56,840
Let me check.

215
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,680
Let me check.

216
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,900
Open your mouth, let me check.

217
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,960
Good, that's a good girl.

218
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,280
That's a good girl.

219
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:10,160
I thought this would be a long process.

220
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,600
But I didn't expect that in less than a year,

221
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:16,520
your mother couldn't take it

222
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,920
and jumped off the building.

223
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,280
I was wrong.

224
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,760
I was really wrong.

225
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,920
But I am your father after all.

226
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:33,520
You are my biological daughter.

227
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:34,440
Child.

228
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:36,640
Don't flatter yourself.

229
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,320
You're not my father.

230
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,400
My father wouldn't do such a thing

231
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:43,280
as murdering his wife.

232
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:45,760
I came here today

233
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,920
not to catch up with you.

234
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:52,720
I'm seeking justice for someone else.

235
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,920
Someone else?

236
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,530
I can choose not to call the police.

237
00:13:58,680 --> 00:13:59,560
Do me a favor.

238
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:01,580
Give me your phone.

239
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,640
Mom.

240
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,800
Are you still in touch with Shen Jingyao?

241
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,640
What happened with Yuran was out of necessity.

242
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:29,240
It's all over now.

243
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:30,640
Why would I contact him?

244
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,610
He wouldn't come here for nothing.

245
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,580
Did this old man

246
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,280
find out about Shen Zhixia

247
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:40,080
and want to extort money from us?

248
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,880
He wants to extort money from us?

249
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:46,100
He's lucky the Lu family didn't sue him for marriage fraud.

250
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,720
Besides,

251
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,960
I kept this tightly under wraps.

252
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,840
There's no reason for it to leak out.

